fields.title: The Humber Swim
fields.intro: Great to see the team at The Humber Swim this weekend
fields.content:
What an amazing day yesterday was at the final Humber Swim of 2021! Thank you to Sarah and Frank Scholes for allowing Urban Attiva and our Wild Swimming Tow Floats to be the official tow float of the event. 
In aid of The Humber Rescue, so far this years swims have raised an impressive 20,000 towards the vital life saving duties they perform, on what is described as one of the most dangerous stretches of water in the world, owing to its strong currents and ever changing sandbanks. 
Well be back next year for the massive 9 swims across the Humber!
